<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-27"><a href="Portage#repoman"><span class="tocnumber">4.15</span> <span class="toctext">repoman</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-28"><a href="Portage#Troubleshooting"><span class="tocnumber">5</span> <span class="toctext">Troubleshooting</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-29"><a href="Portage#Main_.28Gentoo.29_ebuild_repository_sync_time"><span class="tocnumber">5.1</span> <span class="toctext">Main (Gentoo) ebuild repository sync time</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
